w5g">Chu Mạnh Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Th%C3%ADnh-v%C5%A9/poem-idB7vvNQrTeC4ShYbDwdUw">Thính vũ - 聽雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Bao-C%C3%A1t/Th%C3%B9-C%E1%BB%91-Hu%E1%BB%91ng-ki%E1%BA%BFn-k%C3%BD/poem-eQgLS1sfJcNxyuAxOXTwxA">Thù Cố Huống kiến ký - 酬顧況見寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Bao-C%C3%A1t/author-dbuplR6dDRrwJdVAokl1lw">Bao Cát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/V%C4%83n-thi-%C3%B4ng-C%C3%A1t-Xuy%C3%AAn-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-thu-c%E1%BB%ADu-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%ADu-d%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%A1ch-trung-ngo%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BB%87nh-k%C3%BD-th%E1%BB%8B-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ap32-i1W2hfUMoAyyDa8tw">Văn thi ông Cát Xuyên tiên sinh thu cửu nguyệt nhị thập cửu dạ khách trung ngoạ bệnh ký thị kỳ 1 - 聞詩翁葛川先生秋九月二十九夜客中臥病寄示其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Thi%E1%BB%81m/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%E1%BA%A9m-t%E1%BB%ADu/poem-iLKv51XBmYqtBOXWIq2Xow">Xuân nhật ẩm tửu - 春日飲酒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Thi%E1%BB%81m/author-euImnp4iLisTPNWkShmsSA">Bạch Ngọc Thiềm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
